35 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
36 the members of this body congratulate the Georgia Association of Manufacturers upon its
37 125th anniversary and wish GAM and the industry it serves a bright future with "one glorious
38 purpose"–the betterment of humankind.
39 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
40 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
41 Georgia Association of Manufacturers.
